Cemig in Talks to Buy 10% of Belo Monte Dam, Folha Reports

-- B y   J o s e   S e r g i o   O s s e
-- 
2011-10-01T14:57:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-01/cemig-in-talks-to-buy-10-of-belo-monte-dam-folha-reports.html
Cia Energetica de Minas Gerais (CMIG4) , the
Brazilian electric company known as Cemig, is in talks to buy a
10 percent stake in the Belo Monte dam from the companies
building the facility,  Folha de S.Paulo  reported.  The newspaper cited an unidentified person familiar with
the matter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jose Sergio Osse in Sao Paulo at 
 josse1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Helder Marinho at 
 hmarinho@bloomberg.net  